          "url": "https://www.siblingswrite.com/authors/josh"
        }
      ],
      "genre": ["Christmas Fiction", "Holiday Fiction", "Fantasy", "Adventure Fiction", "Family Fiction"],
      "bookFormat": "https://schema.org/Paperback",
      "description": "Join Tim on a captivating adventure of hope, family, and the enduring magic of Christmas. Perfect for fans of holiday adventures and heartwarming tales, this story reminds us that even in the darkest times, the light of Christmas can shine the brightest.",
