---

<PostHogLayout>
  <BaseLayout title={title} description={description} permalink={permalink} current="work">
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(structuredData)} />
    <div class="container-new">
      <h1>Our Work</h1>
      <!-- <figure class="work-image">
        <img src="/assets/work-illustration.webp" alt="Illustration of teamwork" width="330">
      
      </figure> -->
      <p>
        We’re passionate about creating adventurous stories, that spark your imagination and bring joy to our readers. Here's a look at some of the work we’ve done and what we’re currently working on.
      </p>

      <!-- Book Section -->
      <h2>Featured Work</h2>
      <article class="book-section" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Book">
        <img src="/assets/nutcracker.jpg" alt="Book cover for The Battle for Christmas: Reign of the Nutcrackers - A Christmas adventure novel featuring Tim's magical holiday journey" width="200" itemprop="image">
        <div>
          <p><strong itemprop="name">The Battle for Christmas: Reign of the Nutcrackers</strong></br><span itemprop="description">Join Tim on a captivating adventure of hope, family, and the enduring magic of Christmas. Perfect for fans of holiday adventures and heartwarming tales, this story reminds us that even in the darkest times, the light of Christmas can shine the brightest.</span></p>
          <meta itemprop="genre" content="Christmas Fiction">
          <meta itemprop="genre" content="Holiday Fiction">
          <meta itemprop="genre" content="Fantasy">
          <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Battle-Christmas-Reign-Nutcrackers/dp/B0DPKHMYZ1/ref=sr_1_2?crid=I5DWDTES3YWX&dib=eyJ2IjoiMSJ9.DmJrhZrdQtB7pGWH9IvAZKZKTx1gMCkYEPuD3R0WX61de458GtTsEU7eVXeBvtgq-ikR04xVMyItbmk5eu2hRwvXcnlkuTGBT1NyUZ0ZiYjxhNrhle14RDmzfNmve3CsJ0KaCLfWQA8qGiy2wjFdAU6Y-SUqDtIbFA6B3i7DVTkGbbHQNdBib5hfzkTbU-XqEhoNi52bsDk4GLZ95oosu4Wmi-HMtR3h5A-MGwG9Esw.j8WZZczBoKaGv4glN4hzV_Iu_NbsDX8-O58knWrr9Qo&dib_tag=se&keywords=battle+for+christmas&qid=1737934190&sprefix=battle+for+christ%2Caps%2C123&sr=8-2" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="buy-button" itemprop="url">Buy Now on Amazon</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="book-section" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Book">
        <img src="/assets/brownsisland.jpg" alt="Book cover for Escape from Browns Island - A young adult adventure novel featuring 17-year-old Tommy's supernatural encounter on an Ohio River island" width="200" itemprop="image">
        <div>
          <p><strong itemprop="name">Escape from Browns Island</strong></br><span itemprop="description">Every small town has legends—but not every kid gets the chance to rewrite them. This novelette starts off with a simple dare: 17-year-old Tommy must spend one summer night alone on Browns Island, an abandoned, 4-mile-long island in the heart of the Ohio River. What he wants is a peaceful night to himself. What he needs is an escape from the chaos he just caused his family. What he finds is an island that isn't abandoned. It is alive and waiting for his arrival.</span></p>
          <meta itemprop="genre" content="Young Adult">
          <meta itemprop="genre" content="YA Fiction">
          <meta itemprop="genre" content="Teen Fiction">
          <meta itemprop="genre" content="Adventure">
          <meta itemprop="genre" content="Supernatural">
          <a href="https://dub.sh/browns-island" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="buy-button" itemprop="url">Find it Now on Amazon</a>
        </div>
      </article>

      <h2>Other Projects</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong><a href="https://www.amazon.com/Wild-Adventure-Mitch-Sand-Bridge-ebook/dp/B0CJKVK2ZD?ref_=ast_author_dp_rw&dib=eyJ2IjoiMSJ9.StVAtmZ_WxfszMkfO8IdYnWixPuFOSx7YoQ7SNBx0jCwZSEEoXq-bkZV66ABiBf0.P2071nbAUipjZTyl4AfsSG7biKX73gJxnBGXuF1SMyc&dib_tag=AUTHOR">The Wild Adventure of Mitch and the Sand Bridge by Zach Hawrot</a></strong><em> Welcome to summer vacation! The time for good memories, great beaches, and — invasions?</em></li>
        <!-- <li><strong>Project 2:</strong> Community storytelling workshops for aspiring writers.</li>
        <li><strong>Project 3:</strong> Seasonal stories celebrating traditions and togetherness.</li> -->
      </ul>

      <!-- Reader Testimonials -->
      <h2>What Readers Are Saying</h2>
      <div class="testimonials-section">
        <blockquote class="testimonial">
          <p>"Great story. I love the descriptions of the store and the people. It was heart warming.♥️"</p>
          <cite>— Reader of our Short Stories</cite>
        </blockquote>

        <blockquote class="testimonial">
          <p>"Escape from Brown's Island bursts off the page like a star running back on a Saturday-night breakaway—fast, thrilling, and impossible to stop. The Hawrot siblings cut, juke, and power through danger with the perfect mix of grit and finesse, turning every chapter into a game-winning drive. A true end-zone celebration of adventure worthy of the record books."</p>
          <cite>— Reader of Escape from Brown's Island</cite>
        </blockquote>

        <blockquote class="testimonial">
          <p>"I decided to give this book a try over the holiday season and I'm so glad I did! This was a huge break from the normal self-help / non-fiction books I like to read, so I wasn't sure what to expect. The authors do a wonderful job of building a world based on their own lives while pushing into fantasy and adventure in so many creative ways! I couldn't put the book down after the halfway point where the story keeps you guessing while filling you with an undeniable Christmas cheer. I'm a grown adult who felt like a kid again while enjoying this story. I've since passed it along to my own son with the same joy shared by the characters in this book! I hope you enjoy it as much as we do!"</p>
          <cite>— Reader of Battle for Christmas: Reign of the Nutcrackers</cite>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </BaseLayout>
</PostHogLayout>

<style>
  .container-new {
    max-width: 80%;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 2em;
  }

  .work-image {
    float: right;
    margin: -3em -7em 2em 2em;
    max-width: 300px;
  }

  .work-image img {
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5em;
  }

  .book-section {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1em;
    margin: 2em 0;
  }

  .book-section img {
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    margin: 12px
  }

  .buy-button {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 1em;
    padding: 0.8em 1.5em;
    background-color: #007acc;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 4px;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .buy-button:hover {
    background-color: #005fa3;
  }

  .testimonials-section {
    margin-top: 4em;
    padding: 3em 2em;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2em;
    background: rgba(249, 250, 251, 0.8);
    border-radius: 16px;
    border-top: 3px solid var(--primary-color, #548e9b);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }

  .testimonial {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(84, 142, 155, 0.08) 0%, rgba(190, 214, 221, 0.2) 100%);
    padding: 2em;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border-left: 5px solid var(--primary-color, #548e9b);
    margin: 0;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .testimonial:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
  }

  .testimonial p {
    font-size: 0.95em;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #333;
    font-style: italic;
    margin: 0 0 1em 0;
  }

  .testimonial cite {
    font-size: 0.95em;
    color: #666;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 600;
    display: block;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1020px) {
    .work-image {
      float: none;
      margin: 0 auto 2em;
    }

    .book-section {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .book-section img {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 250px;
    }

    .testimonials-section {
      padding: 2em 1.5em;
      margin-top: 3em;
    }
  }
</style>